import React from 'react'
import {Row, Col, Container} from 'react-bootstrap'

function Row1Dashboard() {
    return (
        <Container>
        <Row>
            <Col>1 of 2</Col>
            <Col>2 of 2</Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
            <Col>1 of 3</Col>
            <Col>2 of 3</Col>
            <Col>3 of 3</Col>
        </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Row1Dashboard
